<title>OMRI and Other Excerpts for Armenia: OMRI - 8JAN97 - FRANCE BECOMES CO-CHAIR OF KARABAKH NEGOTIAT</title>
<h1>OMRI - 8JAN97 - FRANCE BECOMES CO-CHAIR OF KARABAKH NEGOTIAT</h1>
<i>eurasia@sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Wed, 08 Jan 97 12:06:34 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#98">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#98">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#98">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#98">[ author ]</a>
