<title>OMRI and Other Excerpts for Armenia: OMRI - 1JAN97 - ARMENIAN PRIME MINISTER ON RELATIONS WITH RU</title>
<h1>OMRI - 1JAN97 - ARMENIAN PRIME MINISTER ON RELATIONS WITH RU</h1>
<i>eurasia@sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Mon, 06 Jan 97 14:30:28 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#94">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#94">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#94">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#94">[ author ]</a>
