<title>OMRI and Other Excerpts for Armenia: OMRI - 20DEC96 - LATEST ISSUE OF OPPOSITION NEWSPAPER CONFIS</title>
<h1>OMRI - 20DEC96 - LATEST ISSUE OF OPPOSITION NEWSPAPER CONFIS</h1>
<i>fsu@mail.sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Fri, 20 Dec 96 14:22:11 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#93">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#93">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#93">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#93">[ author ]</a>
