<title>OMRI and Other Excerpts for Armenia: OMRI - 2DEC96 - ARMENIAN GOVERNMENT GETS A VOTE OF CONFIDENC</title>
<h1>OMRI - 2DEC96 - ARMENIAN GOVERNMENT GETS A VOTE OF CONFIDENC</h1>
<i>eurasia@sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Tue, 03 Dec 96 11:38:55 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#80">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#80">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#80">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#80">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
