<title>OMRI and Other Excerpts for Armenia: OMRI - 25Nov96 - ARMENIAN OPPOSITION DEMANDS FRESH PRESIDENT</title>
<h1>OMRI - 25Nov96 - ARMENIAN OPPOSITION DEMANDS FRESH PRESIDENT</h1>
<i>eurasia@sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Mon, 02 Dec 96 11:35:41 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#76">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#76">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#76">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#76">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
