<title>OMRI and Other Excerpts for Armenia: 6 Nov 96 - More Karabakh Diplomacy</title>
<h1>6 Nov 96 - More Karabakh Diplomacy</h1>
<i>eurasia@sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Thu, 07 Nov 96 11:34:55 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#58">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#58">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#58">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#58">[ author ]</a>
