<title>OMRI and Other Excerpts for Armenia: OMRI--4 Nov 1996--FINNISH FOREIGN MINISTER IN TRANSCAUCASUS</title>
<h1>OMRI--4 Nov 1996--FINNISH FOREIGN MINISTER IN TRANSCAUCASUS</h1>
<i>eurasia@sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Mon, 04 Nov 96 11:51:52 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#56">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#56">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#56">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#56">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0057.html">eurasia@sorosny.org: "OMRI - 5 November - Armenian Prime Minister Resigns"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0055.html">eurasia@sorosny.org: "OMRI--4 Nov--OPPOSITION LEADER ON THE SITUATION IN ARMENIA"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
