<title>OMRI and Other Excerpts for Armenia: OMRI--23 Oct 1996--LEADER OF RULING PARTY ON ARMENIAN PM</title>
<h1>OMRI--23 Oct 1996--LEADER OF RULING PARTY ON ARMENIAN PM</h1>
<i>arichter@sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Wed, 23 Oct 96 09:30:31 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#45">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#45">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#45">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#45">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0046.html">arichter@sorosny.org: "OMRI--23 Oct 1996--KARABAKH ELECTION RUMPUS"</a>
