<title>OMRI and Other Excerpts for Armenia: OMRI--23 Oct 1996--FINAL RESULTS OF ARMENIAN ELECTIONS</title>
<h1>OMRI--23 Oct 1996--FINAL RESULTS OF ARMENIAN ELECTIONS</h1>
<i>arichter@sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Wed, 23 Oct 96 09:29:40 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#44">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#44">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#44">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#44">[ author ]</a>
