<title>OMRI and Other Excerpts for Armenia: OMRI - Oct 9 1996 -- ARM. GOV'T ACCUSED OF RIGHTS VIOLATIONS</title>
<h1>OMRI - Oct 9 1996 -- ARM. GOV'T ACCUSED OF RIGHTS VIOLATIONS</h1>
<i>eurasia@sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Wed, 09 Oct 96 09:19:55 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#34">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#34">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#34">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#34">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
