<title>OMRI and Other Excerpts for Armenia: OMRI--4 OCT 1996--ARMENIAN ELECTORAL COMMISSION REJECTS OSCE</title>
<h1>OMRI--4 OCT 1996--ARMENIAN ELECTORAL COMMISSION REJECTS OSCE</h1>
<i>kkhalmatov@sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Mon, 07 Oct 96 09:59:15 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#33">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#33">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#33">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#33">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0034.html">eurasia@sorosny.org: "OMRI - Oct 9 1996 -- ARM. GOV'T ACCUSED OF RIGHTS VIOLATIONS"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0032.html">eurasia@sorosny.org: "OMRI--2 0CTOBER 1996--MANUKYAN ABJURES VIOLENCE"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
