<title>OMRI and Other Excerpts for Armenia: OMRI--2 0CTOBER 1996--MANUKYAN ABJURES VIOLENCE</title>
<h1>OMRI--2 0CTOBER 1996--MANUKYAN ABJURES VIOLENCE</h1>
<i>eurasia@sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Thu, 03 Oct 96 14:23:13 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#32">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#32">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#32">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#32">[ author ]</a>
