<title>OMRI and Other Excerpts for Armenia: OMRI--1 October 1996 -- TER-PETROSSYAN SOFTENS RHETORIC</title>
<h1>OMRI--1 October 1996 -- TER-PETROSSYAN SOFTENS RHETORIC</h1>
<i>eurasia@sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Tue, 01 Oct 96 12:19:35 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#30">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#30">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#30">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#30">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0031.html">eurasia@sorosny.org: "OMRI--3 Oct 1996--OSCE CASTS DOUBTS ON ARMENIAN PRES. POLL"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0029.html">tlankina@sorosny.org: "OMRI--30 September 96--COMMISSION UPHOLDS TER-PETROSSYAN'S E"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
