<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0030.html">eurasia@sorosny.org: "OMRI--1 October 1996 -- TER-PETROSSYAN SOFTENS RHETORIC"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0028.html">tlankina@sorosny.org: "OMRI--25 September 96--TER-PETROSSYAN LEADS IN ARMENIAN PRES"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
