<title>OMRI and Other Excerpts for Armenia: OMRI--29 August 96--ARMENIA HEAVILY DEPENDENT ON FOREIGN AID</title>
<h1>OMRI--29 August 96--ARMENIA HEAVILY DEPENDENT ON FOREIGN AID</h1>
<i>tlankina@sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Fri, 30 Aug 96 09:20:30 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#9">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#9">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#9">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#9">[ author ]</a>
