<title>OMRI and Other Excerpts for Armenia: OMRI--14 August 96--ASTRONOMER AMBARTSUMYAN DIES</title>
<h1>OMRI--14 August 96--ASTRONOMER AMBARTSUMYAN DIES</h1>
<i>tlankina@sorosny.org</i><br>
<i>Wed, 14 Aug 96 11:03:27 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#2">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#2">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#2">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#2">[ author ]</a>
