<title>Groong Network: Noyan Tapan News (January 10)</title>
<h1>Noyan Tapan News (January 10)</h1>
<i>nt-send@nt.arminco.com</i><br>
<i>Fri, 10 Jan 1997 21:50:13 +0300 (MSK)</i>
<p>
