           N O Y A N  T A P A N   H E A D L I N E S<br>
                               <br>
                     ( January 10, 1997 )<br>
<p>
-------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>
<p>
<p>
   ARMENAIN SOCIAL INVESTMENT FUND TO RESTORE ANOTHER SCHOOL<br>
                    IN THE EARTHQUAKE ZONE<br>
                               <br>
  FIRST ALL-ARMENIAN SPORTS GAMES TO COME OFF IN YEREVAN NEXT<br>
                             FALL<br>
                               <br>
  CDRF ACCEPTED MOLECULE RESEARCH PROGRAM THAT WAS PRESENTED<br>
                    BY ARMENIAN SCIENTISTS<br>
