<title>Groong Network: Patriarch's Christmas greetings</title>
<h1>Patriarch's Christmas greetings</h1>
Asbed Bedrossian (<i>asbed@skat.usc.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Wed, 8 Jan 97 13:00:39 PST</i>
