<title>Groong Network: Gregorian to leave Brown for Carnegie</title>
<h1>Gregorian to leave Brown for Carnegie</h1>
Horizon Online (<i>72263.1572@CompuServe.COM</i>)<br>
<i>Tue, 7 Jan 97 12:47:24 PST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#277">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#277">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#277">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#277">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0278.html">Armen Martirossyan: "From Radio Liberty Homepage"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0276.html">Asbed Bedrossian: "OMRI Digest 1/6/96"</a>
