<title>Groong Network: Avedis Tevanian leads Mac OS development team</title>
<h1>Avedis Tevanian leads Mac OS development team</h1>
Vachik Hacopian (<i>vhacopian@WELLESLEY.EDU</i>)<br>
<i>Tue, 7 Jan 97 1:14:59 PST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#274">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#274">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#274">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#274">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0275.html">Mher Sassouni: "Turkey/CenAsia Highlights 10/21/96"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0273.html">Horizon/Giro Manoyan: "Armenian premier leaves for Washington"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
