For further information/application forms contact:<br>
<p>
Prof. Gareguin Markarian<br>
Dept. of Enginnering<br>
Lancaster University<br>
Lancaster LA1 4YR UK<br>
e-mail: G.Markarian@lancaster.ac.uk<br>
<p>
or <br>
<p>
Dr Manook Soghomonian<br>
Samsung Research Centre<br>
The Communications House<br>
Staines, Middlesex TW18 4QE UK<br>
e-mail: Manook_S@moose.co.uk<br>
