Dear Groong and Hayastan readers,<br>
<p>
I'm happy to announce that we have pledged enough to fund a year's<br>
worth of Noyan Tapan news on Groong, plus a little more.<br>
<p>
Many of the 143 contributors have requested anonymity. For this reason<br>
I'll keep the rest of the details off the lists, and we will hopefully<br>
see Noyan Tapan posts on Groong as soon as the financial details<br>
progress.<br>
<p>
I'll contact those who came forward with pledges off the lists, and<br>
I'll communicate further details separately.<br>
<p>
Thank you all who came forward to help. I shall not close the fund drive<br>
officially, because I'd like to continue the funding process further, in<br>
order to extend our ability to receive news-for-pay for many more months,<br>
and not go through another fund-drive 9-10 months from now. Therefore, I<br>
include the original pledge for help below.<br>
<p>
In the meantime, Shnorhavor Nor Dari yev Sourp Dznount to all, may you<br>
all live long and prosper in 1997 and beyond.<br>
<p>
Regards,<br>
<p>
Asbed<br>
