-----------------------------------------------------------------<br>
                             Headlines<br>
                 Aragil Electronic News Bulletin,                <br>
                 Issue 1158, Tuesday 31 Dec. 1996                <br>
                     Digest of Armenian press                    <br>
-----------------------------------------------------------------<br>
<p>
                          Dear readers,                          <br>
                   H A P P Y   N E W   Y E A R!                  <br>
<p>
Topics:<br>
=================================================================<br>
          POLITICS<br>
          --------<br>
1. Prime Minister Is Satisfied By His First Official Visit To Russia<br>
2. Prime Minister Plans To Visit The USA In The Beginning Of Year <br>
3. Seven Agreements Have Been Signed Between Armenia And Iran<br>
<p>
          MISCELLANEOUS<br>
          -------------<br>
4. President Created A Commission To Celebrate Charents' 100th Anniversary<br>
