<title>Groong Network: Wind of gale force damages Armenian regions.</title>
<h1>Wind of gale force damages Armenian regions.</h1>
Giro Manoyan (<i>72263.1572@CompuServe.COM</i>)<br>
<i>Mon, 30 Dec 96 13:48:35 PST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#240">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#240">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#240">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#240">[ author ]</a>
