<title>Groong Network: OSCE Minsk group co-chairman to meet Azerbaijani ...</title>
<h1>OSCE Minsk group co-chairman to meet Azerbaijani ...</h1>
Kevork K. Oskanian (<i>100436.3410@compuserve.com</i>)<br>
<i>Sat, 28 Dec 1996 06:36:08 -0500</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="index.html#232">[ date ]</a><a href="thread.html#232">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#232">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#232">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0233.html">Horizon Online: "Artcile in the Montreal Gazette"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0231.html">Kevork K. Oskanian: "VOA/Russia/Muslims"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
</ul>
<!-- body="start" -->
      BAKU, December 28 (Itar-Tass) - Russian co-chairman of the OSCE Minsk<br>
<p>
group for Nagorno-Karabakh Yuri Yukalov will meet Azerbaijan's President <br>
Geidar Aliyev and Foreign Minister Gasan Gasanov in Baku on Saturday. <br>
Yukalov arrived here on Friday after concluding consultations with <br>
Armenia in Yerevan and Hankendi. <br>
   The Russian diplomat and the Azerbaijani leaders are expected to discuss<br>
<p>
the Kharabakh settlement process after the OSCE summit in Lisbon, futher <br>
activities of the Minsk group and the date for the next round of the <br>
Armenian-Azerbaijani negotiations. <br>
   pan/gor <br>
<!-- body="end" -->
