<!-- body="start" -->
-----------------------------------------------------------------<br>
                            Headlines                            <br>
                 Aragil Electronic News Bulletin,                <br>
                Issue 1156, Saturday 28 Dec. 1996                <br>
                     Digest of Armenian press                    <br>
-----------------------------------------------------------------<br>
<p>
Topics:<br>
