TENDER PARTICIPATION FEE (DRAMS)        656,050<br>
INITIAL PRICE (DRAMS)                   13,121,000<br>
BID SUBMISSION DEADLINE                 20 JAN 1997<br>
DATE OF TENDER                          24 JAN 1997<br>
