<p>
<p>
                  KARABAKH PRESIDENT SWORN IN<br>
                               <br>
     JUDGE HAKOBIAN COMMENTS ON CRIMINAL CASE AGAINST IM's<br>
                            EX-AIDE<br>
                               <br>
     DEFENDANT ARAM PETROSSIAN INVITES PRESIDENT TO BE HIS<br>
