New- Spring 1997 Schedule of Courses<br>
<p>
The Spring 1997 Armenian Studies Program Schedule is now on our World<br>
Wide Web page. A wide variety of courses in language, art, history,<br>
literature, and culture will be offered. <br>
<p>
New- November 1996 Issue of Hye Sharzhoom<br>
<p>
The November 1996 (Vol. 18, no.1 ) issue of Hye Sharzhoom/Armenian<br>
Action is now on-line. Read about the many activities of the Armenian<br>
students Organization and the Armenian Studies Program. Interesting<br>
articles on Armenian agriculture and a new art school are featured. If<br>
you would like to be added to the mailing list (free subscription)<br>
send us your name and address.<br>
