Date: Tue, 10 Dec 1996 13:21:28 PST<br>
<p>
  	  				 <br>
	 YEREVAN (Reuter) - Armenia's Supreme Court on Tuesday  <br>
sentenced three members of the outlawed Dashnaktsitun political <br>
party to death on terrorism charges. <br>
	 Judge Eduard Manukyan said Armen Mndjoyan, Arsen Arsrune and  <br>
