	 ANKARA, Dec 12 (Reuter) - Turkish President Suleyman Demirel  <br>
has written to the 15 leaders of European Union countries to ask <br>
them not to forget Turkey's bid for full membership when they <br>
meet at the Dublin summit, an aide said on Thursday. <br>
	 ``The EU will talk about its future enlargement at the Dublin  <br>
